        "actionName": "ai.ask",
        "input": {
          "input": "Concept: {{ trigger[\"nodeText\"] }}\nCurrent pipeline stage note: {{ trigger[\"nodeNote\"] }}",
          "prompt": "You are the Pipeline Orchestrator for a math game studio. A game concept's GO/NO-GO decision has just been updated.\n\nThe pipeline stages in order are:\nstage-idea → stage-spec → stage-precheck → stage-delight → stage-design → stage-overlap → stage-gono → stage-p1 → stage-p2a → stage-p2b → stage-p3 → stage-p4 → stage-p5\n\nRules:\n- If GO/NO-GO = GO and current stage is 'stage-gono', advance to 'stage-p1'\n- If GO/NO-GO = GO and current stage is any earlier stage, advance to the next stage in sequence\n- If GO/NO-GO = Revise, keep same stage\n- If GO/NO-GO = Pause, keep same stage\n- If GO/NO-GO = NO-GO, keep same stage (revision logic will handle it)\n- If GO/NO-GO = Pending, keep same stage\n\nRespond with ONLY the exact stage ID string (e.g. stage-p1) and nothing else."
        }
      }
